description: Fresh and bursting with flavor is what Saussibun has to offer. Serving the Houston, TX area we provide great tasting food that's prepared fresh with the highest quality of ingredients. Treat yourself today with a truly authentic German meal from our delicious menu. At Saussibun you are sure to enjoy the great flavors, friendly service, and affordable prices.Take your taste buds on an unforgettable journey with Saussibun!
